    "desc": "Articles of Style provides an online bespoke menswear service for gentlemen of all shapes & sizes who want to improve their style and live their best lives.",
    "navbar": "SHOP\nEXPLORE\nSIGN IN",
    "text": "Book a Zoom Appointment\nSHOP\nEXPLORE\nSIGN IN\nCustom Wardrobes\nPersonal styling & bespoke tailoring by America’s best-dressed man\nLearn More\nPERSONAL STYLING\nWe help you design a stylish & versatile wardrobe that is built just for you\nBESPOKE FIT\nWe make sure your fit is perfect with our exclusive bespoke fiting process\nQUALITY TO LAST\nWe handcraft your garments to the highest quality in our New York tailor shop\nBest Sellers\nSignature Performance Hopsack Suit\n$2,895\n+1 more\nSignature Fresco Trouser\n$795\n+10 more\nSignature Wool & Linen Jacket\n$2,395\n+2 more\nHarris Tweed Shacket\n$895\n+6 more\nHOW IT WORKS\n01\n02\n03\n04\n05\n1. Choose Fabrics & Designs\nArticles of Style is a full-service bespoke tailor shop, online.\nStart by choosing your fabrics and customizing your garments, then create your AOS account.\nSHOP\nWe help you create\nYour Dream Wardrobe\nwith the right fit, the right fabrics and the right designs - for YOU.\nABOUT US\nRecent Articles\nAOS Upgrade: Spencer MacIntyre\nWe recently worked with Spencer MacIntyre; an up-and-coming actor from Toronto.  Spencer has been going to a lot...\nRead More\nMore Fabrics Options\nLooking for a specific color, pattern or fabric? No problem! We've created personal relationships with the best fabric...\nRead More\nThe Most Interesting Menswear in the World\nIf you’ve been anywhere near a television in the past three years, you probably recognize our guest today....\nRead More\nSee All Articles\nLet's talk about your wardrobe...\nBook a Zoom Appointment\nStyle Guide\nWardrobe Packages\nAbout Us\nHow It Works\nBest Sellers\nArticles\nVideos\nContact Us\nCustomer Reviews\nWeddings\nFrequently Asked Questions\nReturn Policy\nGift Cards\nBook a Zoom Appointment\nEnter your email to receive Dan Trepanier's free e-book \"10 Rules for Style\"\nSubmit\n© ARTICLES OF STYLE 2022\nPRIVACY POLICY / TERMS OF SERVICE / RETURN POLICY",
    "font": "Lato, sans-serif",
